Description:
🍓 Berry Protein Smoothie
A refreshing smoothie packed with antioxidants & protein!

🔹 Ingredients:

1 cup almond milk (or milk of choice)
½ cup frozen mixed berries
1 banana
1 scoop vanilla protein powder
1 tbsp chia seeds
Handful of spinach (optional, but great for nutrients!)
🔹 Instructions:
1️⃣ Blend all ingredients until smooth.
2️⃣ Pour into a glass & enjoy!

🔥 Perfect for a post-workout boost or a quick breakfast!

 #recipe #recipeideas #recipeshare #smoothie #cfxfitness

🥗 Grilled Chicken & Quinoa Power Bowl
A high-protein, nutrient-packed meal for all-day energy!

🔹 Ingredients:
1 grilled chicken breast, sliced
½ cup cooked quinoa
1 cup mixed greens
¼ avocado, sliced
¼ cup cherry tomatoes, halved
1 tbsp feta cheese (optional)
Dressing: Olive oil + lemon juice + salt & pepper

Instructions:
1️. Assemble all ingredients in a bowl.
2️. Drizzle with dressing and mix well.

💪 Simple, satisfying, and full of flavor!

#CFXFitness #CFXEats #Recipeoftheday #Healthyrecipe

🌮 Healthy Turkey & Veggie Tacos
Taco night, but make it healthy! 🌮✨

🔹 Ingredients:

1 lb ground turkey
½ onion, diced
1 bell pepper, chopped
1 zucchini, diced
1 tsp chili powder
½ tsp cumin
½ tsp garlic powder
4 small whole-wheat tortillas
Toppings: Avocado, salsa, Greek yogurt, cilantro
🔹 Instructions:
1️⃣ Sauté onion, bell pepper, and zucchini until soft.
2️⃣ Add ground turkey & seasonings, cook until browned.
3️⃣ Spoon into tortillas & add your favorite toppings!

🔥 Delicious, high-protein, and packed with veggies!

#CFXEats #CFXFitness #recipe #healltyfood #Recipeoftheday
